HEADWORD: Shopkeeper
<hw>Shop"keep`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A trader who
sells goods in a shop, or by retail; -- in distinction from one who
sells by wholesale.</def> <rj><au>Addison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

